overview:
Pachelbel is inspired in creating and making vegan fashion a new trend to harmonize fashion demands on designs, quality materials and credible workmanship with the need to maintain animal sustainability in this modern and conscious society.

Our fashion products are made of materials like bicast leather, polyurethane leather, vinyl polymer, nylon and jacquard embroidery with in-house designed fittings to bring out the uniqueness of each design, and the character its carries and represents to attract and fascinate our valuable customers for a value that they owned is worthy and enduring with time and occasion.
